msgid ""
"For more <filename>/etc/dhcp3/dchpd.conf</filename> options see the <ulink "
"url=\"http://manpages.ubuntu.com/manpages/lucid/en/man5/dhcpd.conf.5.html\">d"
"hcpd.conf man page</ulink>."
