"often this may be enough. If the server has a large amount of data a more "
"robust rotation scheme should be used."
msgstr ""
"Le script shell de la section <xref linkend=\"backup-shellscripts\"/> ne "
"vous donne qu'un jeu de sauvegardes hebdomadaire. Ceci peut être suffisant "
